author: isurues
msg: Fixing https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AXIS2-4101. Removed support for other extensions inside the repository/services folder. This is beacuese, we can't select the correct deployer only by looking at the file extension. And also, removed unwanted map in DeploymentEngine which keeps a 1 to 1 mapping (which is no longer valid) between the extension and the deployer. Changed a test case also to match the change..
